                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5614" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0231</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7612 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">均衡至精，拉动求益：SP公司在制品积压的纾解之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Balance and Pull production to Lean: The Way to Ease the Overstock of Work in Process in SP Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薛建武，曹金锦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安三平智能科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在制品积压；价值流分析；均衡生产；看板拉动</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Work in Process Backlog, Value Stream Analysis, Balanced Production, Kanban Pull</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在制品积压是当前汽车零部件制造业面临的普遍难题，激烈的市场竞争迫使企业转型升级解决在制品积压问题，持续降低在制品库存控制成本。SP公司主要生产橡胶流体产品，其复杂的工艺流程、混合的制造方式与多样化的客户需求使得生产线上产生了大量的在制品库存。本案例针对SP公司生产线上在制品积压的问题，描述了企业在集团公司精益数字化转型的背景下，通过分析在制品积压的根本原因、选择在制品控制策略、制定在制品控制方案的步骤,结合精益生产工具降低在制品库存的过程。引导读者对在制品积压的问题进行系统思考，熟悉其解决思路与工具。具体了解在制品积压原因分析的方法、在制品库存控制策略的选择，并掌握运用均衡生产与看板拉动这两种精益生产的工具进行在制品库存控制的流程与方法。以期提高学生理论联系实际、解决企业现实问题的能力 。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Work in Process (WIP) backlog is a common problem facing the auto parts manufacturing industry at present. The fierce market competition forces enterprises to transform and upgrade to solve the problem of WIP backlog and continue to reduce the cost of WIP inventory control. SP produces rubber fluid products, and its complex processes, mixed manufacturing methods and diverse customer requirements have resulted in a large WIP inventory on the production line. This case focuses on the backlog of WIP on the production line of SP Company, under the background of lean digital transformation of group companies, describes the process of reducing WIP inventory by analyzing the root cause of WIP backlog, selecting WIP control strategy, and formulating WIP control scheme with lean production tools. Guide readers to systematically think about the backlog of WIP and get familiar with its solutions and tools. Specifically understand the reason analysis method of WIP backlog, the selection of WIP inventory control strategy, and master the process and method of WIP inventory control by using balanced production and Kanban pull, the two lean production tools. The aim is to improve students&#39; ability to combine theory with practice and solve practical problems in enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《生产与运作管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务市场细分、服务战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-10</td>
                            </tr>
